ABOUT ŌSUMI
Ōsumi, \”dwell\” in Japanese, is an elevated Japanese-American fusion restaurant with a touch of Latin flair. Located in the heart of Coral Gables on beautiful, pedestrian Giralda Plaza, Ōsumi delights the senses with its impeccable food, signature drinks, and sophisticated setting.
BOOK A TABLE

PRIVATE DINING
& EVENTS
Host your next corporate or social event in our private dining space.
Our private dining room offers guests a highly exclusive experience tucked away behind a grand sliding door and furnished with its own private bar and butler service, an intimate oasis awaits.
The space seats up to 16 guests
Can be expanded to include an adjacent dining area, which seats up to 28 guests (44 guests in total).
Ōsumi’s Special Events Team will make your celebration an experience to be remembered by you and your guests.
